{"tid":2398450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吃菜？吃驚！ 越南巨乳網紅教下廚 觀眾全失焦","createTime":"2021-02-07T10:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:06:18.000Z","uid":337052,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"56b1e9cf0590084d8eaf1f53e77e362b77ee9d26","tid":2398450,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">吃菜？吃驚！ 越南巨乳網紅教下廚 觀眾全失焦</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/07/phpxpbcIe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F07%2FphpxpbcIe.png&h=66c9af38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越南網紅武黃玉（見圖）穿著清涼、在YouTube頻道教人煮飯。（圖擷取自V&otilde; Huỳnh Ngọc Phụng Youtube頻道）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/07 17:48<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕越南網紅武黃玉（Pong Kyubi）身材姣好，向來以作風大膽、「大尺度」聞名，例如她在YouTube頻道推出教人做菜的影片，不僅上身只穿著肚兜，而且還是若隱若現的薄紗，引起許多議論。<br />\n<br />\n據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，<span class=\"red\">武黃玉在烹飪頻道中穿著清涼，影片內的「巨乳」呼之欲出，還有許多「邪惡的視角」，若隱影若現、又好像要露點，因此引發網友直呼「不知道是烹飪課，還是在玩JAV遊戲」。</span><br />\n<br />\n網友看到影片後，網友留言說「每月支付網路費來觀看，這樣的影片真是物超所值」、「有沒有來這而不看烹飪」、「這道菜很好吃，但我不知道我是在看食物，還是因為衣服...」。<br />\n<br />\n據知，<span class=\"red\">武黃玉出席胡志明市會展中心舉行的「2019年越南車展」時，疑似因刻意穿幫「露點」的行動，引發許多人批評，還因此丟了工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ezyj8OOKtNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fezyj8OOKtNk&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=abc2e8d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ezyj8OOKtNk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435095&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=454ba191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435095&h=52cab5b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435095</a>"},{"pid":"a62c27a588afdf227f0e0808ce922be5f736d83b","tid":2398450,"uid":4574,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"Ban <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddf0624bae937c77623b8f710b9ae0d5ce1c8a7","tid":2398450,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"完全無法注意在食物上"},{"pid":"6072e2af51e18b6b2b63b52d86770bbebfc68b0e","tid":2398450,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"></span>"},{"pid":"85041dab566cd5bc8a4e3496b46a97cced4ac181","tid":2398450,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"萬刀甲出動!"},{"pid":"80bc7ca06f4322f8da77d003d767df6e362c7b55","tid":2398450,"uid":158411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"boom boom how much?"},{"pid":"99893966d68af092f64dc441bfb327d1bf60455a","tid":2398450,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85041dab566cd5bc8a4e3496b46a97cced4ac181","tid":2398450,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"萬刀甲出動!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"万刀甲可以收收皮先"},{"pid":"73f3f4c06324ce3eb93d5b50a7c9ceb2d6027680","tid":2398450,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"膊頭橫過唔少港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d77e0afda9ec12bb4178047de6788c243481833","tid":2398450,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"全身都假嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前post過有啲相好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"